    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good overall condition and has been consistently well-maintained. The engine is reliable, starting up without hesitation, and the transmission provides smooth gear shifts for a comfortable drive. While the exterior and interior show some minor signs of normal wear consistent with its age, the car remains clean and presents well. It is a dependable choice for anyone looking for a solid, road-ready vehicle that has been cared for properly.",
